Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.81,FT-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chce sa biť?" pýta sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.08,FT-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Snaž sa, Natsu!
